ui_cookie_main_text: Your privacy is very important! No personal data is stored on this website and no cookies are used. For purely technical reasons, only local storage is used to remember your language selection.
ui_cookie_faq_reply_1: Cookies are small text files / data packages that are created by a web browser and websites to store individual user data
ui_cookie_faq_reply_2: Local Storage provides storage without an expiration date in the user's browser - for example to improve the loading time of the website.
ui_cookie_faq_reply_3: Vercel Analytics is capable of capturing and displaying data such as page views, visitor numbers, dwell time, errors, and latency times.
